menu "VoiceStick app diagnostics"

config VOICESTICK_BUTTON_DIAGNOSTIC_ON_BOOT
    bool "Run raw button GPIO diagnostic on boot"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, firmware logs raw primary/secondary button level changes
        for a short period after boot. This is intended for bench testing new
        board ports and is disabled in normal builds.

config VOICESTICK_BLE_AUDIO_E2E_TEST_ON_BOOT
    bool "Run BLE audio end-to-end diagnostic on boot"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, firmware waits for the BLE central to subscribe to
        state and audio notifications, then simulates one short primary-button
        hold to exercise the normal recording and BLE audio path. This is
        intended for automated bench testing only and is disabled in normal
        builds.

endmenu
